leadership-approach|vision_results_people_process|application_2|2|Stabilise with Results, then add People|Before you move on, use Results to turn the conversation into a named decision, owner, and follow-up point. Then bring in People to check how the decision is landing and what communication will support commitment. This gives the work a stronger middle step before you rely on the full pattern.|results|active|leadership-approach::vision_results_people_process::application_2
